            Please note that our bonus is NOT STICKY!<br>
            Winning the bonus is NOT LIMITED!
          </mj-text>
        </mj-column>
      </mj-section>


      <mj-section full-width="full-width" padding="16px 0 0">
        <mj-column width="100%" padding="0">
          <mj-text mj-class="fontSizeText-16 light" align="left">
